page_data_script:
products = frappe.get_all(
    "Item", 
    filters={"custom_publish_to_website": 1}, 
    fields=["name", "item_name", "item_code", "image", "standard_rate", "custom_route", "item_group"], 
    ignore_permissions=True
)

default_currency = frappe.db.get_single_value("Global Defaults", "default_currency")


for product in products:
    product["standard_rate"] = frappe.utils.fmt_money(product["standard_rate"], currency=default_currency)
    
categories = frappe.get_all(
    "Item Group",
    filters={"custom_publish_to_website": 1}, 
    fields=["name", "item_group_name", "image", "custom_route"], 
    ignore_permissions=True
)

banner_slider_doc = frappe.get_all(
    "Website Slideshow", 
    filters={"custom_show_in": "Home Banner"},
    fields=['name'],
    ignore_permissions=True
)

banner_sliders = frappe.get_all(
    "Website Slideshow Item",
    fields=["heading", "description", "image", "url"], 
    filters={
        "parent": banner_slider_doc[0]
    },
    order_by="idx",
    ignore_permissions=True
)

data.products = products
data.categories = categories
data.banner_sliders = banner_sliders

data.page_data = {
    "products": products
}
